================================================================================
liminal-experiment
================================================================================

KEYBINDINGS
-----------

Escape     - quit
Mouse      - rotational movement
W, A, S, D - translational movement
Click      - interact
T          - toggle flashlight
Y          - toggle noclip
LShift     - sprint
LCtrl      - crouch
+          - increase look sense
-          - lower look sense

